erver logic and web infrastructure."}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-4"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Server"}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"The Forgotten Server 1.4.2"}],["$","br",null,{}],"The core engine of the game, written in C++. Responsible for all game logic, including monster behavior, NPC interactions, and map loading. Every gameplay mechanic runs through this layer."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-4"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Database"}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"MySQL"}],["$","br",null,{}],"Handles all persistent data storage — player accounts, character progression, inventory, and world state. Both the game server and the website communicate directly with this database."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-4"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Web & Account System"}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"NGINX + MyAcc (Gesior)"}],["$","br",null,{}],"The website is powered by the open-source MyAcc panel by Gesior, served through NGINX. Players can create accounts, manage characters, and access game information through this interface."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-4"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Game Client"}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"OTClient by MEHAH"}],["$","br",null,{}],"The open-source game client used by players to connect to the server. It communicates with The Forgotten Server via ",["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"TCP protocol on port 7171"}],", sending and receiving real-time game packets for movement, combat, chat, and all in-game interactions."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-4"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Development Tools"}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"RME — Map Editor"}],["$","br",null,{}],"Used to design and edit the entire game world. Map files are exported directly and loaded by the server."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"text-primary","children":"Object Builder"}],["$","br",null,{}],"Used to create and manage all visual assets — sprites and object definitions (.spr / .dat). These files are used by both the server and the client to render the game world correctly."]}],["$","hr",null,{"className":"border-t-2 border-foreground/20 my-4"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-primary border-b-2 border-primary pb-1","children":"Tech Stack"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"overflow-x-auto","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full border-collapse border-2 border-foreground text-sm","children":[["$","thead",null,{"className":"bg-primary text-black","children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"className":"border border-foreground px-4 py-2 text-left","children":"Layer"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"border border-foreground px-4 py-2 text-left","children":"Technology"}],["$","th",null,{"className":"border border-foreground px-4 py-2 text-left","children":"Role"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr","Game Engine",{"className":"border-b border-foreground/30 even:bg-foreground/5","children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-foreground/30 px-4 py-2","children":"Game Engine"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-foreground/30 px-4 py-2 text-primary font-bold","children":"